---
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
import "../styles/about-page.css";
---

<Layout
  title="About Me"
  description="Learn more about Amr Riyad - Software Engineer"
  tags={[]}
>
  <div class="bio-section">
    <h2>Hello, I'm Amr Riyad</h2>
    <p class="bio-intro">
      A Software Engineer passionate about creating efficient, scalable backend
      solutions. I thrive on solving complex problems and building systems that
      make a difference.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="timeline-section">
    <h2>My Journey</h2>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <h3>
          Software Engineer <span class="company"
            >@ <a
              href="https://alsun.ai/"
              target="_blank"
              style="text-decoration: none;">Alsun AI</a
            ></span
          >
        </h3>
        <p class="timeline-period">May 2025 - Current</p>
        <p class="timeline-description">TBC</p>
        <div class="tech-used">
          <span>Python</span>
          <span>React</span>
          <span>Docker</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <h3>
          Software Engineer <span class="company"
            >@ <a
              href="https://yomaak.com/"
              target="_blank"
              style="text-decoration: none;">Yomaak</a
            ></span
          >
        </h3>
        <p class="timeline-period">January 2025 - May 2025</p>
        <p class="timeline-description">
          Migrated WordPress website to a Fastify/React/Tailwind stack,
          enhancing platform performance and scalability. Integrated Stripe's
          API to automate subscription billing and recurring payments,
          streamlining invoicing.
        </p>
        <div class="tech-used">
          <span>React</span>
          <span>Fastify</span>
          <span>Tailwind</span>
          <span>Stripe</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <h3>
          Back End Developer <span class="company"
            >@ <a
              href="https://www.instabug.com/"
              target="_blank"
              style="text-decoration: none;">Instabug</a
            ></span
          >
        </h3>
        <p class="timeline-period">July 2024 - September 2024</p>
        <p class="timeline-description">
          Optimized the Jenkins CI/CD backend pipeline by enabling concurrent
          execution of test specs, reducing overall execution time by 60%.
          Enhanced the Ruby on Rails test suite, cutting test execution time by
          20%. Implemented auto-deletion of expired documents to optimize
          storage.
        </p>
        <div class="tech-used">
          <span>Ruby on Rails</span>
          <span>Jenkins</span>
          <span>CI/CD</span>
          <span>MySQL</span>
          <span>Redis</span>
          <span>Docker</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline-item">
      <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <h3>
          Computer Science Degree <span class="company">@ Cairo University</span
          >
        </h3>
        <p class="timeline-period">September 2020 - June 2025</p>
        <p class="timeline-description">
          Bachelor of Computer Science from the Faculty of Computers and
          Artificial Intelligence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="achievements-section">
    <h2>Recognition & Open Source</h2>
    <div class="achievement-cards">
      <div class="achievement-card">
        <a
          href="https://icpc.global/ICPCID/S0FHPJBI2OJR"
          target="_blank"
          class="achievement-card-link"
        >
          <h3>ICPC</h3>
          <p>Qualified for the 2023 ACPC Finals in Egypt.</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="achievement-card">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/sqlancer/sqlancer/issues?q=is%3Apr%20author%3A%40me%20state%3Amerged"
          target="_blank"
          class="achievement-card-link"
        >
          <h3>SQLancer</h3>
          <p>
            I contributed to an open-source tool called SQLancer, which is used
            for automated testing of database management systems to detect bugs.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="achievement-card">
        <a
          href="https://facebook.com/codingcompetitions/hacker-cup/2022/certificate/433728468200425"
          target="_blank"
          class="achievement-card-link"
        >
          <h3>Meta Hacker Cup</h3>
          <p>
            Reached Round 2 of the Meta Hacker Cup 2022, an international
            competitive programming competition organized by Meta (formerly
            Facebook).
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="achievement-card">
        <a
          href="https://www.facebook.com/icpcfcaicu"
          target="_blank"
          class="achievement-card-link"
        >
          <h3>ICPC FCAI-CU</h3>
          <p>
            Led training for 1,000+ students in competitive programming,
            mentored 200+ in data structures and algorithms using C++, and
            served as a problem setter and judge for ECPC.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="skills-section">
    <h2>Coding Spellbook</h2>

    <div class="skills-container">
      <div class="skill-category">
        <h4>Languages</h4>
        <hr />
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span>Python</span>
          <span>C/C++</span>
          <span>Ruby</span>
          <span>Golang</span>
          <span>SQL</span>
          <span>TypeScript</span>
          <span>HTML/CSS</span>
          <span>Dart</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h4>Frameworks</h4>
        <hr />
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span>Fastify</span>
          <span>React</span>
          <span>Ruby on Rails</span>
          <span>Django</span>
          <span>FastAPI</span>
          <span>Flutter</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h4>Technologies</h4>
        <hr />
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span>Docker</span>
          <span>Redis</span>
          <span>Elasticsearch</span>
          <span>Jenkins</span>
          <span>Git</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <h4>Core Skills</h4>
        <hr />
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span>RESTful APIs</span>
          <span>Algorithms</span>
          <span>OOP</span>
          <span>Design Patterns</span>
          <span>Databases</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
